us</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>“A film that single-handedly changed the way we perceive storytelling, its relationship with the visual medium and the narrative language of cinema itself. This is where the movies’ long love affair with the grammar of time started.” <strong>Rahul Desai</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>“It’s hard to think of a more perfect film about the focal role of storytelling in the construction of human society.” <strong>Vigen Galstyan</strong></p>\r\n","quote":null,"credits":{"director":"Akira Kurosawa","producer":"Jinkichi Minoru, Sojiro Motoki","writer":"Akira Kurosawa, Shinobu Hashimoto","featuring":"Toshiro Mifune, Machiko Kyo, Takashi Shimura"},"year":"1950","nameAndYear":"Rashomon (1950)","links":{"player":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscription/film/watch-rashomon-1950-online","southbank":""},"player":{"url":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscription/film/watch-rashomon-1950-online","cta":"https://player.bfi.org.uk/subscribe/5647","pillar":"subscription","price":0,"duration":0},"performances":[],"tags":["BFI Player"],"productionCountries":"Japan","runningTime":83,"sightAndSound":{"results":[{"position":41,"tied":true,"category":"critics"},{"position":20,"tied":true,"category":"directors"}],"voters":null},"products":[]},{"uuid":"489eada8-7d7e-594c-acac-5903f43f4b85","image":{"base":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/","relative":"2021-03/vertigo-1958-012-madeleine-bouquet_1000x750.jpg","main":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-03/vertigo-1958-012-madeleine-bouquet_1000x750.jpg/1920x1080-cropped/vertigo-1958-012-madeleine-bouquet_1000x750.jpg","thumb":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-03/vertigo-1958-012-madeleine-bouquet_1000x750.jpg/960x540-cropped/vertigo-1958-012-madeleine-bouquet_1000x750.jpg","preload":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2021-03/vertigo-1958-012-madeleine-bouquet_1000x750.jpg/96x54-cropped/vertigo